ETHICAL USE & SAFETY ADDENDUM:

⚠️  IMPORTANT SAFETY WARNINGS:

1. EPILEPSY WARNING: This toolkit can generate rapidly flashing images that
   may trigger photosensitive epilepsy. Always include proper warnings.

2. PSYCHOLOGICAL IMPACT: Some attacks (hypnosis, subliminal messaging) may
   cause discomfort or psychological effects. Use with caution.

3. SYSTEM STABILITY: Window bomb and memory exhaustion attacks can crash
   systems. Only use in controlled environments.

ETHICAL GUIDELINES:

- For authorized security research only
- Obtain proper permissions before testing
- Include safety warnings with all outputs
